{"tid":715214,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"唐詩詠：揀男友難過買樓","createTime":"2018-06-24T09:59:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T03:07:20.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2680a4d022c92cbe581989c8f380bde541b5d742","tid":715214,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T09:59:11.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】唐詩詠、莊思敏昨日出席海外物業投資活動，詩詠表示一直有在香港睇樓，但睇中的樓盤都太貴：「曾睇中一間dream house，2000幾萬元900幾呎，實在太貴了，要再努力一下，惟有向海外發展，我終於明白馬國明為甚麼睇了幾年樓才決定買，因為要睇得多才知甚麼是好。」問她買樓難還是揀男朋友難？她笑言揀男友更難，因為揀樓都會找到心儀單位，但男友要多方面配合，未必可以自己話事。<br />\n<br />\n莊思敏在港擁有2個物業放租，幸未遇過租霸，笑指最麻煩其實是租給家人或朋友，因為他們都會要求多多，不過她揀男友就不需要對方有樓在手，最重要是對她好，亦不介意用自己單位做愛巢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Etj0qTRTbxwEOTVkVA9Eog--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjY3O2g9MTAwMDtpbD1wbGFuZQ--/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/D03d_ENP02P07240618copy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FEtj0qTRTbxwEOTVkVA9Eog--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjY3O2g9MTAwMDtpbD1wbGFuZQ--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2FD03d_ENP02P07240618copy.jpg&h=a319a230&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%94%90%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%A0-%E6%8F%80%E7%94%B7%E5%8F%8B%E9%9B%A3%E9%81%8E%E8%B2%B7%E6%A8%93-220518817.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2594%2590%25E8%25A9%25A9%25E8%25A9%25A0-%25E6%258F%2580%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%258F%258B%25E9%259B%25A3%25E9%2581%258E%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E6%25A8%2593-220518817.html&d=1SWaFfpca83OCmV2nzhWpP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0d805911\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%94%90%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%A0-%E6%8F%80%E7%94%B7%E5%8F%8B%E9%9B%A3%E9%81%8E%E8%B2%B7%E6%A8%93-220518817.html</a>"},{"pid":"9238a257329b80278be27b80d33d8ae946535234","tid":715214,"uid":138067,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T10:07:33.000Z","msg":"老得滯無人要咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gi